projects.name: Coinbase Clone
projects.tech: Metamask - Next.js - Sanity.io - thirdweb - Vercel - React
projects.description: A Coinbase Clone that allows you to send money to different MetaMask wallets! The front end is built with Next.js and the back end is Sanity.io, I used styled components for the styling and used thirdweb to handle the blockchain. I also used MetaMask for the authentication and deployed using Vercel! Let me know what you think!
